dutch	nehyph96.tex	nl[_NL]	ec
=====
^^e4 -> ä adieresis
^^e7 -> ç ccedilla
^^e8 -> è egrave
^^e9 -> é eacute
^^ea -> ê ecircumflex
^^eb -> ë edieresis
^^ef -> ï idieresis
^^ee -> î icircumflex
^^f1 -> ñ ntilde
^^f6 -> ö odieresis
^^fc -> ü udieresis
^^fb -> û ucircumflex

patterns can be loaded as ec only, and the same patterns are usable under texnansi as well (same position of letters)


